        <description>&lt;img src="https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/Image.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Narrative Design and Visual Storytelling in Ori" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;This article offers an insight into the framework of UE, by analyizng the steps to take when an UE game is launched.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;visual-storytelling&#34;&gt;Visual Storytelling&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;developing-a-consistnet-visual-vocabulary-for-a-sequence&#34;&gt;Developing a Consistnet Visual Vocabulary for a Sequence&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;direction-indicates-theme&#34;&gt;Direction indicates Theme&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Left&lt;/strong&gt; = &lt;code&gt;the past&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;security&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;what is known&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Right&lt;/strong&gt; = &lt;code&gt;the future&lt;/code&gt;, &lt;code&gt;uncentainty&lt;/code&gt;, or &lt;code&gt;the unknown&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;Example&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/1.JPG&#34;
	width=&#34;1212&#34;
	height=&#34;542&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/1_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_71341_480x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 480w, https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/1_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_71341_1024x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;223&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;536px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the beginng, Ori is beckoned by Gumo to the cave on the left, which is an familiar from the first game, as if returning to the past.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/2.JPG&#34;
	width=&#34;1214&#34;
	height=&#34;551&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/2_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_83346_480x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 480w, https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/2_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_83346_1024x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;220&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;528px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then ori exits the cave and a big seasonal montage begins, where we have sweeping camera with a strong rightward momentum.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/3.JPG&#34;
	width=&#34;1196&#34;
	height=&#34;530&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/3_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_66628_480x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 480w, https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/3_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_66628_1024x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;225&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;541px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The narration tells player that the answer to help Ku lay in the past, so Ori returns back to the left.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/4.JPG&#34;
	width=&#34;1204&#34;
	height=&#34;531&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/4_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_60950_480x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 480w, https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/4_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_60950_1024x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;226&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;544px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once retrieved the item, Ori backs right to Ku. Then we begin the journey into will of the wisps.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;seasonal-montage&#34;&gt;Seasonal Montage&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/5.JPG&#34;
	width=&#34;1237&#34;
	height=&#34;633&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/5_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_82869_480x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 480w, https://PureWhite216.github.io/p/narrative-design-and-visual-storytelling-in-ori/5_huaf34fbf3356fec395b028e0610cff063_82869_1024x0_resize_q75_box.JPG 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;195&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;469px&#34;
	
&gt;
Create a balance between what is nostalgic and what is new.
The montage takes player back to the familiar scenes in blind forest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;narrative-design&#34;&gt;Narrative Design&lt;/h1&gt;</description>
